description:
Danny recaps this week's Lohan Beach Club with comedians/friends Jenna Brister & Johnno Wilson. They try to make sense of the puzzle that is Lindsay Lohan. This week she rehired May, fired Jules, and mind-f*cked the rest of the cast/viewing audience. They also briefly discuss this season of MTV's The Challenge.


*This week's #RHOBH recap is available for free at Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
